 Robinson]]\n* [[Ginger Rogers]]\n* [[Will Rogers]]\n* [[Cesar Romero]]\n* [[Mickey Rooney]]\n* [[Rosalind Russell]]\n* [[Randolph Scott]]\n* [[Sebastian Shaw (actor)|Sebastian Shaw]]\n* [[Norma Shearer]]\n* [[James Stewart]]\n* [[Barbara Stanwyck]]\n* [[Margaret Sullavan]]\n* [[Robert Taylor (actor)|Robert Taylor]]\n* [[Shirley Temple]]\n* [[The Three Stooges]]\n* [[Spencer Tracy]]\n* [[John Wayne]]\n* [[Orson Welles]]\n* [[Mae West]]\n* [[Ed Wynn]]\n* [[Loretta Young]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n<gallery widths=\"190\" perrow=\"5\">\nFile:Laurel & Hardy in Flying Deuces 1 edited.png|[[Laurel & Hardy]] in their film \"[[The Flying Deuces]]\" (1939)\nFile:Shirleytemple young.jpg|[[Shirley Temple]], 1933\nFile:Marlene Dietrich (26).jpg|[[Marlene Dietrich]], 1932\nFile:Clark Gable as Rhett Butler in Gone With the Wind trailer.jpg|[[Clark Gable]] as [[Rhett Butler]] in the trailer for ''[[Gone with the Wind (film)|Gone with the Wind]]'' (1939)\n</gallery>\n{{-}}\n\n=== Filmmakers ===\n[[Image:Walt Disney Snow white 1937 trailer screenshot (13).jpg|right|150px|thumb|Walt Disney introduces each of the Seven Dwarfs in a scene from the original 1937 [[Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs (1937 film)|''Snow White'']]]]\n* [[Walt Disney]]\n* [[Alfred Hitchcock]]\n* [[Fritz Lang]]\n* [[John Ford]]\n* [[Cecil B. DeMille]]\n* [[Frank Capra]]\n* [[Jean Renoir]]\n* [[Ernst Lubitsch]]\n* [[William Wyler]]\n* [[Howard Hawks]]\n* [[Victor Fleming]]\n* [[George Cukor]]\n* [[Michael Curtiz]]\n* [[Josef von Sternberg]]\n\n===Musicians===\n\n{|\n| valign = top |\n* [[Lale Anderson]]\n* [[Harold Arlen]]\n* [[Louis Armstrong]]\n* [[Fred Astaire]]\n* [[Count Basie]]\n* [[Dalida]]\n* [[Cab Calloway]]\n* [[Eddie Cantor]]\n* [[Nat King Cole]]\n* [[No\u00ebl Coward]]\n* [[Bing Crosby]]\n* [[Vernon Duke]]\n* [[Jimmy Durante]]\n* [[Duke Ellington]]\n* [[Ella Fitzgerald]]\n* [[George Gershwin]]\n* [[Ira Gershwin]]\n* [[Benny Goodman]]\n* [[Coleman Hawkins]]\n* [[Billie Holiday]]\n| valign = top |\n* [[Pete Johnson]]\n* [[Louis Prima]]\n* [[Artie Shaw]]\n* [[Big Joe Turner]]\n* [[Les Brown (bandleader)|Les Brown]]\n* [[Lena Horne]]\n* [[Al Jolson]]\n* [[Jerome Kern]]\n* [[Lead Belly]]\n* [[The Ink Spots]]\n* [[Glenn Miller]]\n* [[Earl Hines]]\n* [[\u00c9dith Piaf]]\n* [[Cole Porter]]\n* [[Ma Rainey]]\n* [[Django Reinhardt]]\n* [[Bill Robinson|Bill \"Bojangles\" Robinson]]\n* [[Rodgers and Hart]]\n* [[Frank Sinatra]]\n* [[Bessie Smith]]\n* [[Fats Waller]]\n* [[Ethel Waters]]\n|}\n\n===Influential artists===\n==== Painters and sculptors ====\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Jos\u00e9 Clemente Orozco]]\n*[[Anni Albers]]\n*[[Josef Albers]]\n*[[Hans Arp]]\n*[[Milton Avery]]\n*[[Romare Bearden]]\n*[[Paula Modersohn-Becker]]\n*[[Max Beckmann]]\n*[[Thomas Hart Benton (painter)|Thomas Hart Benton]]\n*[[Max Bill]]\n*[[Isabel Bishop]]\n*[[Marcel Breuer]]\n*[[Patrick Henry Bruce]]\n*[[Paul Cadmus]]\n*[[Marc Chagall]]\n*[[John Steuart Curry]]\n*[[Salvador Dal\u00ed]]\n*[[Stuart Davis (painter)|Stuart Davis]]\n*[[Charles Demuth]]\n*[[Otto Dix]]\n*[[Theo van Doesburg]]\n*[[Arthur Dove]]\n*[[Marcel Duchamp]]\n*[[Max Ernst]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[David Alfaro Siqueiros]]\n*[[Philip Evergood]]\n*[[Lyonel Feininger]]\n*[[Joaqu\u00edn Torres Garc\u00eda]]\n*[[Alberto Giacometti]]\n*[[Arshile Gorky]]\n*[[John D. Graham]]\n*[[George Grosz]]\n*[[Philip Guston]]\n*[[Marsden Hartley]]\n*[[Hans Hofmann]]\n*[[Edward Hopper]]\n*[[Johannes Itten]]\n*[[Frida Kahlo]]\n*[[Wassily Kandinsky]]\n*[[Ernst Ludwig Kirchner]]\n*[[Paul Klee]]\n*[[Oskar Kokoschka]]\n*[[K\u00e4the Kollwitz]]\n*[[Willem de Kooning]]\n*[[Walt Kuhn]]\n*[[Jacob Lawrence]]\n{{col-3}} \n*[[Tamara de Lempicka]]\n*[[Fernand L\u00e9ger]]\n*[[Andrew Loomis]]\n*[[Reginald Marsh (artist)|Reginald Marsh]]\n*[[Andr\u00e9 Masson]]\n*[[Henri Matisse]]\n*[[Joan Mir\u00f3]]\n*[[Piet Mondrian]]\n*[[Gabriele M\u00fcnter]]\n*[[Georgia O'Keeffe]]\n*[[Francis Picabia]]\n*[[Pablo Picasso]]\n*[[Horace Pippin]]\n*[[Diego Rivera]]\n*[[Ben Shahn]]\n*[[Charles Sheel